variables.name: filter7
variables.value:
CASE WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."LOEKZ") = 1 THEN 'not deleted'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'S' THEN 'locked'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'
     ELSE "EKPO"."LOEKZ"
END

variables.name: filter6
variables.value:
CASE
    WHEN ISNULL("LFA1"."VBUND") = 1 THEN 'External'
    ELSE 'Internal'
END

variables.name: automation_rate
variables.value: AVG(CASE WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 1 THEN NULL WHEN "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" = 'B' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END)

variables.name: change_rate
variables.value: 1.0*COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."CHANGE_NUMBER") = 0 THEN "EKPO"."MANDT"||"EKPO"."EBELN"||"EKPO"."EBELP" ELSE NULL END)/COUNT_TABLE("EKPO")
